Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.70,0:00:21.66,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:17705,21668}Whenever my feelings were hurt,\NI couldn't see anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.66,0:00:25.58,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:21668,25588}because I held a lie in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.58,0:00:29.55,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:25588,29551}Time moved faster than I could react,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.55,0:00:34.59,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:29551,34597}so I pulled myself away\Nfrom everything, but now
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.59,0:00:40.64,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:34597,40645}I can't stop anything at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.06,0:00:47.61,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:41062,47610}Accepting everything, I rise up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.57,0:00:53.49,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:49571,53491}I'll fly over all of time\Nwhile holding onto your presence,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.49,0:00:56.99,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:53491,56995}following the trace of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.99,0:01:03.00,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:56995,63001}My world becomes engulfed with light.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.46,0:01:09.25,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:65461,69257}A never ending sky,\Nyour never changing eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.25,0:01:12.96,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:69257,72969}I want to love these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.96,0:01:19.35,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:72969,79350}No matter the distance,\Nor if we are separated
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.35,0:01:22.77,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:79350,82770}we are always connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.06,0:01:29.44,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:87066,89444}Want you here tonight!
Comment: 0,0:01:31.11,0:01:31.11,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:91112,91112}Part A
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.99,0:01:40.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:96993,100580}How about going to buy chocolate\Nafter school today?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.58,0:01:43.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:100580,103124}It's almost Valentine's Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.12,0:01:46.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:103124,106336}I'll have to give some\Nobligation chocolates this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.96,0:01:48.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:106961,108755}Meimi, you're going too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.75,0:01:51.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:108755,111674}Valentine's. What shall I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.67,0:01:54.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:111674,114552}Aren't you giving\NAsuka Jr. chocolate?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.92,0:01:56.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:114927,116679}What? You're kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.67,0:01:59.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:116679,119724}What's that?\NIs that how you really feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.72,0:02:04.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:119724,124062}Someone's giving me chocolate?\N"True love" chocolate?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.06,0:02:08.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:124062,128066}You've got it wrong!\NIt's obligation chocolate!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.56,0:02:10.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:128566,130193}I don't care which it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.19,0:02:14.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:130193,134781}but a better gift would be\Na meat bun or octopus fritters.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.78,0:02:19.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:134781,139035}What a kid! Valentine chocolates\Naren't a 3:00 snack!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.03,0:02:22.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:139035,142121}You won't get any\N"true love" chocolates!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.12,0:02:25.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:142121,145416}– Be quiet!\N– What do you mean, be quiet?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.41,0:02:28.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:145416,148086}– What's it to you?\N– What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.08,0:02:29.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:148086,149629}Jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.42,0:02:32.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:150421,152799}Asuka, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.09,0:02:38.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:154092,158054}That's no way to treat a lady.\NYou've got to be gentle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.47,0:02:43.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:160473,163101}It's Tooru Ijuin!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.10,0:02:45.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:163101,165978}Hey, who's Tooru Ijuin\Nsupposed to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.97,0:02:49.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:165978,169941}You don't know?\NRight now, Tooru Ijuin is…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.48,0:02:53.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:170483,173695}…an ultra-popular guy\Namong the freshmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.69,0:02:57.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:173695,177699}Sure! He models, always\Nin the latest magazines.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.69,0:03:01.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:177699,181202}Then how could such a guy\Nknow Asuka Jr.?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.20,0:03:02.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:181202,182912}Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.62,0:03:06.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:183621,186708}Oh, good morning!\NI'm a freshmen in class A.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.33,0:03:09.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:187333,189377}Tooru Ijuin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.96,0:03:16.88,saint tail default,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:193965,196884}The Heart Thief on\NSt. Valentine's Day!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.01,0:03:27.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:202014,207937}Just know that I'm not friends with\Nthis guy. We live near each other—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.93,0:03:31.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:207937,211816}That's mean!\NWe played a lot together as children.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.81,0:03:33.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:211816,213317}Be quiet, don't follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.40,0:03:38.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:214402,218281}In the first place, you're younger!\NSo why are you bigger than me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.03,0:03:43.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:220032,223327}Asuka, you're at it again?\NHe's always like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.32,0:03:47.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:223327,227248}He absolutely despises\Nmy good looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.00,0:03:53.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:231002,233171}Pardon me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.17,0:03:55.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:233171,235381}– You're Tooru Ijuin, right?\N– Yes, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.79,0:03:59.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:235798,239385}– Isn't she from another school?\N– I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.92,0:04:04.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:239927,244015}– Please enjoy these cookies I made.\N– Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.01,0:04:07.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:244015,247143}And will you let me\Ntake your picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.14,0:04:09.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:247143,249562}– Sure.\N– Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.56,0:04:15.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:249562,255318}Wait a minute! I look best diagonally\Nfrom the right, at a 30-degree angle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.31,0:04:18.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:255318,258571}– Okay! I understand.\N– And also this… – I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.19,0:04:21.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:259197,261949}This is stupid.\NLet's go and leave this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.94,0:04:23.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:261949,263117}You're so handsome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.45,0:04:26.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:265453,266496}Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.33,0:04:30.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:267330,270458}Hey, wait for me, Asuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.04,0:04:34.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:271042,274796}Asuka! Please wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.79,0:04:36.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:274796,276422}Yeah, just like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.88,0:04:41.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:276881,281969}"There is nothing stronger\Nthan a mother's love."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.96,0:04:44.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:281969,284347}"I am prepared for anything."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.84,0:04:50.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:285848,290812}"The mountain that you see\Nover there is Mt. Asahi."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.52,0:04:53.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:291521,293773}Well, we shall stop here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.77,0:04:58.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:293773,298778}We will have a test next week\Non today's lesson. Review it well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.77,0:05:02.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:298778,302782}– What?\N– You're joking!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.62,0:05:17.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:312625,317421}Can you lend me your English notebook?\NI didn't take any notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:18.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:317421,318965}Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.96,0:05:22.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:318965,322635}Hey, Tooru! Hurry up\Nor I'll leave without you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.63,0:05:25.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:322635,325930}Yeah. Give me a minute!\NIs it no?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.63,0:05:28.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:326639,328474}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.81,0:05:34.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:332812,334939}Here, this is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.35,0:05:37.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:335356,337400}Thank you!\NI'll return it tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.90,0:05:47.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:342905,347034}This is the English notebook.\NWait! That's the wrong one!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.03,0:05:53.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:350037,353499}Oh, no, what am I going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.87,0:05:59.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:355877,359964}– What? You're gonna buy that much?\N– But they're all obligations.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.96,0:06:02.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:359964,362592}And who's the true love?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.59,0:06:06.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:362592,366721}That's a secret!\NAnd, Meimi, what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.72,0:06:08.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:366721,368139}What? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.68,0:06:16.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:372685,376439}– Who'd give him anything?\N– Meimi, how about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.43,0:06:18.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:376439,378608}That's my secret too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.81,0:06:21.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:378816,381527}Unfair, you've all got secrets!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:24.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:381527,384697}– So, Ryoko, what's yours?\N– You mean me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.69,0:06:28.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:384697,388743}You keep asking about us,\Nbut what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.74,0:06:32.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:388743,392288}Isn't it obvious? It's…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.28,0:06:33.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:392288,393873}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.87,0:06:35.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:393873,395374}A secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.25,0:06:44.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:401255,404091}So you lent him\Nthe wrong notebook?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.38,0:06:46.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:404383,406552}Yes, exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.55,0:06:53.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:406552,413059}That notebook is the one I use as a diary\Nto write my daily thoughts in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.43,0:07:02.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:415436,422360}In that notebook, I've written\Nmany poems thinking about Tooru.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.48,0:07:07.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:423486,427073}If Tooru should see any of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.07,0:07:12.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:427073,432286}I'd be so embarrassed\NI wouldn't be able to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.74,0:07:17.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:432745,437750}Don't worry.\NI'm sure God will lend you a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.50,0:07:29.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:446509,449220}Get a notebook back\Nfrom Tooru Ijuin?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.80,0:07:32.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:449804,452348}Right. And it has to be today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.34,0:07:36.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:452348,456185}Before he gets a chance\Nto look at that notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.43,0:07:38.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:456435,458145}Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.14,0:07:42.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:458145,462441}Kanako Shimamura\Nis in love with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.44,0:07:45.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:462441,465820}But she's afraid to have him find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.82,0:07:51.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:465820,471158}This would be the chance to tell him.\NAnd it's almost Valentine's Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.57,0:07:54.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:471575,474453}You may be right, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.28,0:08:01.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:475287,481752}{\i1}A boy as popular as Tooru would\Nnever even give me a second thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.75,0:08:05.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:481752,485798}{\i1}And I'm happy just\Nto be able to look at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.67,0:08:12.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:486674,492096}There are many girls who are unable\Nto honestly display their feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.09,0:08:13.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:492096,493514}Meimi, you're probably…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.39,0:08:17.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:496392,497601}Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:22.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:498060,502481}I understand. Right!\NSt. Tail is a supporter of girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.48,0:08:25.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:502481,505818}I will get that notebook\Nback for Kanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.81,0:08:27.82,saint tail sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:505818,507820}Art Room
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.40,0:08:35.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:513409,515286}Let's clean up quickly and go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.28,0:08:35.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:515286,515786}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.24,0:08:41.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:519248,521584}Jeez, what a filthy classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.88,0:08:48.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:527882,528632}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.09,0:08:57.05,saint tail sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:533095,537058}The brush changes the word\N"notebook" to spell "heart".
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.05,0:08:58.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:537058,538517}Ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.93,0:09:00.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:539935,540561}It's a…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.60,0:09:07.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:541604,547443}"Tonight I will be stealing\NTooru Ijuin's heart away. – St. Tail"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.36,0:09:11.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:549361,551822}His heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.82,0:09:14.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:551822,554241}What about his heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.24,0:09:19.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:554241,559914}– What are you doing here?\N– Let's go home together, Asuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.91,0:09:22.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:559914,562500}Never mind that. Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.33,0:09:28.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:563334,568464}"Tonight I will be stealing\NTooru Ijuin's heart away. – St. Tail"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.17,0:09:31.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:569173,571967}– What's this about?\N– That's my question!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:36.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:574345,576347}What does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.34,0:09:40.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:576347,580518}If it says "heart"…\NYou're kidding! My heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.51,0:09:45.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:580518,585856}This heart? She's gonna perform\Nopen-heart surgery on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.85,0:09:50.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:585856,590319}Of course not, you idiot!\NThink seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.31,0:09:54.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:590319,594698}For example, maybe you have\Na pet cat or dog named Heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.69,0:09:57.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:594698,597284}No, only a turtle named Samantha.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.28,0:09:57.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:597284,597910}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.41,0:10:00.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:598410,600913}Then what could it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.91,0:10:04.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:600913,604375}What could St. Tail\Nwant to steal from you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.45,0:10:06.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:605459,606877}Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.88,0:10:12.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:609880,612633}Heart, heart, heart…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.63,0:10:15.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:612633,615845}That's it!\NI know what it is, Asuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.22,0:10:19.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:616220,619890}What is it?\NWhat's she gonna steal?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.89,0:10:21.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:619890,621851}– To put it simply…\N– Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.85,0:10:26.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:621851,626230}St. Tail has fallen in love\Nwith me, and tonight she's coming
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.23,0:10:29.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:626230,629984}to flirt with me\Nand steal my heart away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.98,0:10:31.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:629984,631527}Think seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.52,0:10:33.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:631527,633237}I'm serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.23,0:10:37.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:633237,637032}Besides, what else could\N"steal my heart away" mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.70,0:10:40.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:637700,640286}Stupid. That's just stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.74,0:10:44.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:640744,644206}Asuka, what are you\Nso upset about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.20,0:10:49.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:644206,649003}Asuka! Could you be jealous\Nof how I attract all the girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.00,0:10:50.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:649003,650671}Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.67,0:10:53.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:650671,653966}{\i1}That St. Tail, with a guy like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.96,0:10:56.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:653966,656510}I, Tooru Ijuin…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.96,0:11:00.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:656969,660055}…shall allow my heart\Nto be stolen with pleasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.30,0:11:05.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:663309,665686}– What's wrong?\N– Don't talk to me!
