Comment: 0,0:11:11.69,0:11:11.69,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:671692,671692}Eyecatch B
Comment: 0,0:11:16.69,0:11:16.69,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:676697,676697}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.07,0:11:25.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:683078,685164}Hey, wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.95,0:11:28.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:685956,688584}Where are you taking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.58,0:11:31.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:688584,691170}Where else? To buy a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.17,0:11:34.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:691170,694632}We're going to buy a present\Nto give St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.88,0:11:38.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:694882,698344}A present? Look here!\NWhat are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.05,0:11:43.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:699053,703807}St. Tail is coming to steal\Nmy heart away, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.80,0:11:47.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:703807,707102}Wouldn't it be rude\Nnot to be prepared for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.60,0:11:50.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:707603,710314}Imbecile! She's a thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.31,0:11:54.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:710314,714568}Never mind. Just tell me\Nwhat gift would make her happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.56,0:11:56.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:714568,716612}How should I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.82,0:12:04.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:719823,724370}Okay, I can't be\Ndragging my feet here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.71,0:12:14.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:732711,734838}That wonderful chocolate smell!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.83,0:12:16.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:734838,736298}Don't look yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.29,0:12:19.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:736298,739885}Why? What's wrong with it?\NDelicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.13,0:12:24.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:740135,744390}I said no. I haven't put\Nthe finishing touch on it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.76,0:12:26.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:744765,746892}The finishing touch?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.06,0:12:30.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:748060,750854}A special ingredient.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.23,0:12:34.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:751230,754608}With lots of love! Sprinkle!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.60,0:12:36.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:754608,756443}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.86,0:12:41.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:757861,761031}You're right. This is delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.03,0:12:44.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:761031,764451}– Isn't it?\N– I wonder why.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.57,0:12:50.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:766578,770791}Listening to them is embarrassing.\NDon't you think, Ruby?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.62,0:12:57.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:773627,777089}I know, right?\NValentine's Day…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.08,0:13:00.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:777089,780009}Ruby, do you have someone\Nto give chocolates to?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.56,0:13:20.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:796567,800446}I've been waiting for you.\NWell? Don't I look great?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.15,0:13:24.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:801155,804450}Hey, what are you up to, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.45,0:13:26.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:804450,806660}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.66,0:13:30.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:806660,810914}This is the proper etiquette\Nfor receiving a lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.24,0:13:35.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:812249,815753}Kanako, it's dinnertime!\NCome down here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.96,0:13:39.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:816962,819131}Yes! I'll be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.05,0:13:48.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:825054,828891}Oh, Lord, forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.93,0:13:54.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:833937,834897}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.23,0:13:58.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:837232,838567}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.56,0:14:02.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:840569,842654}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.75,0:14:19.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:856752,859838}Please be careful, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.21,0:14:22.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:860214,862341}Yes, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.71,0:14:28.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:864718,868305}May the blessings of God be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.06,0:14:37.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:874061,877856}You can stay,\Nbut please don't get in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.85,0:14:40.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:877856,880275}Yeah, yeah. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.94,0:14:44.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:880943,884822}{\i1}St. Tail, come if you dare.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.82,0:14:47.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:884822,887616}{\i1}I'll get you for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.61,0:14:50.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:887616,890536}{\i1}Who would give St. Tail\Nto a creep like him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.91,0:14:52.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:890911,892204}My style!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.08,0:14:55.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:894081,895249}She's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.04,0:14:57.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:896041,897167}Wait, Tooru!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.08,0:14:59.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:898085,899253}Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.58,0:15:03.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:902589,903465}What's the matter, Tooru?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.63,0:15:08.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:905634,908679}It's a present, Asuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.43,0:15:14.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:910431,914143}Wait a minute, idiot!\NDon't bring that in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.76,0:15:17.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:914768,917396}But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.31,0:15:22.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:918313,922359}What did I tell you?! Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.15,0:15:28.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:926155,928073}It's about time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.61,0:15:32.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:930617,932828}Quick! Open the window!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.83,0:15:36.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:934830,936790}Is that you, St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.58,0:15:38.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:937583,938667}{\i1}This must be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.00,0:15:41.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:939001,941503}St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.75,0:15:45.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:941753,945090}Please steal my heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.59,0:15:48.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:946592,948677}Why are you running away?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.67,0:15:50.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:948677,950596}{\i1}What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.97,0:15:53.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:950971,953557}Where are you?\NWhere did you go, St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.14,0:15:56.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:954141,956018}Please steal my heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.51,0:15:58.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:956518,958729}What? Steal your heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.81,0:16:01.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:959813,961190}St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.14,0:16:06.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:962149,966987}Stop it! I'm not St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.07,0:16:10.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:968071,970282}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.40,0:16:13.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:971408,973118}Hold it, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.24,0:16:15.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:974244,975120}St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.87,0:16:21.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:977873,981084}Do you love Tooru that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.62,0:16:23.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:981627,983837}{\i1}What's he mixed-up about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.08,0:16:28.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:985088,988050}I'm taking the notebook,\Njust as I told you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.63,0:16:30.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:988634,990552}{\i1}Notebook?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.14,0:16:40.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:995140,1000479}{\i1}Oh, it was not "heart",\Nit was "notebook".
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.85,0:16:42.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1000854,1002064}See you around!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.06,0:16:44.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1002064,1004650}I won't let you get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.65,0:16:46.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1004650,1006235}Asuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.61,0:16:56.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1014618,1016078}St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.99,0:16:59.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1016995,1019081}Steal my heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.54,0:17:11.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1028549,1031718}– You're in the way!\N– No, you're in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.71,0:17:15.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1031718,1035222}I'm gonna catch St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.22,0:17:17.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1035222,1037516}Asuka, up ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.81,0:17:27.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1043814,1047276}My heart, please steal it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.32,0:17:35.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1052322,1055492}{\i1}I'm pretty sure that\NKanako's house is in this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.53,0:17:42.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1060539,1062249}St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.45,0:17:47.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1064459,1067504}Please wait! My heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.50,0:17:50.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1068505,1070966}Something's going on outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.67,0:17:52.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1070674,1072718}{\an8}St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.21,0:17:54.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1073218,1074428}I'll go look.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.18,0:18:07.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1086189,1087608}Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.15,0:18:11.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1089151,1091111}Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.87,0:18:23.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1101872,1103957}I give you my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.95,0:18:25.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1103957,1105876}Tooru.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.46,0:18:34.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1112466,1114343}You're cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.22,0:18:39.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1117220,1119348}I've made up my mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.22,0:18:46.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1125228,1126271}{\i1}Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.44,0:18:51.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1130442,1131943}Hold it, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.15,0:18:59.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1138158,1139451}What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.20,0:19:07.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1146208,1147250}{\i1}Now you're caught!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.37,0:19:10.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1149378,1150545}Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.59,0:19:20.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1157594,1160222}I'll remember this, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.22,0:19:24.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1160222,1164184}You won't get away\Nfrom me next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.95,0:19:46.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1180951,1186331}What happened to you yesterday?\NYou said you'd buy chocolate with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.33,0:19:49.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1186331,1189918}Oh, sorry about that!\NSomething urgent came up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.00,0:19:55.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1191002,1195340}Good morning, Asuka Jr.!\NSt. Tail got away again?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.34,0:19:59.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1195340,1199428}Be quiet! I almost had her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.42,0:20:04.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1199428,1204808}If only that ship hadn't passed!\NNext time, I'll get her for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.80,0:20:08.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1204808,1208854}Asuka! Asuka, good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.10,0:20:11.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1210105,1211148}Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.98,0:20:14.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1212983,1214526}Kanako?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.52,0:20:15.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1214526,1215444}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.77,0:20:19.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1215777,1219781}– Where are your glasses?\N– I changed to contact lenses.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.78,0:20:22.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1219781,1222993}She's much cuter this way, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.66,0:20:27.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1224661,1227706}Hey, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.70,0:20:31.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1227706,1231293}My heart was stolen,\Njust like the notice said.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.29,0:20:32.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1231293,1232878}By St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.87,0:20:35.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1232878,1235547}Of course not! By Kanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.54,0:20:36.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1235547,1236798}Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.71,0:20:42.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1237716,1242304}You better hurry too,\Nor you'll be late for school.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.80,0:20:44.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1242804,1244222}– But…\N– Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.22,0:20:46.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1244222,1246099}What a guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.09,0:20:49.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1246099,1249644}We're the happiest people alive!
